methods.description:
Attaches the provided Service to the `websub:Listener` with custom `websub:SubscriberServiceConfiguration`.
```ballerina
check websubListenerEp.attachWithConfig('service, {
   target: "http://0.0.0.0:9191/common/discovery",
   leaseSeconds: 36000
}, "/subscriber");
```

